{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"5567d55aea","title":"毛泽东会见法国总统蓬皮杜谈话记录的节选","origin":"根据文件的翻印件打印","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"300a0af732","index":0,"year":1973,"month":9,"day":12,"articleId":"5567d55aea"}],"tags":[{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"38d4b46158","type":"title","text":"毛泽东会见法国总统蓬皮杜谈话记录的节选","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"5567d55aea"},{"id":"17825bd58d","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：（对蓬）我这个人文化不行，不懂外交。","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"5567d55aea"},{"id":"543a438e7f","type":"paragraph","text":"蓬：但是你很了解中国人民。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"5567d55aea"},{"id":"2b946cbe44","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：了解一些，不完全了解。我年纪大了，搞了一些官僚主义。（对齐）也叫BUREAUCRATISM（官僚主义）吗？","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"5567d55aea"},{"id":"5302dd1641","type":"appellation","text":"齐：对，英文是BUREAUCRATISM（官僚主义）。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"5567d55aea"},{"id":"eeed15ac43","type":"paragraph","text":"蓬：但是你过去也从事了很多活动。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"5567d55aea"},{"id":"02e5b1c1dc","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：哎呀，打了二十几年仗了，把精力也耗费得差不多。我是一个小学教员。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"5567d55aea"},{"id":"5505b485c4","type":"paragraph","text":"蓬：我也是教员。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"5567d55aea"},{"id":"7ff54140c8","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：他当过中学教员。","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"5567d55aea"},{"id":"c18e3193cd","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：我是PRIMARY SCHOOL TEACHER（小学教员），形势把我逼去打仗。那么要打呢，就打吧。一打就是二十几年。后头还跟美国人在朝鲜打了一仗。更蒋介石打得多了。跟日本人打了八年。所以外国人到中国，现在这个时代比较难。中国人打游击战争可以。（蓬笑）","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"5567d55aea"},{"id":"89d843f910","type":"paragraph","text":"蓬：我曾有机会见到这两个大国的领导人，他们宣布自己是爱好和平的。我认为他们有理由现在成为爱好和平的人。","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"5567d55aea"},{"id":"8caf2bf259","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：我不信。","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"5567d55aea"},{"id":"7da6bc1625","type":"paragraph","text":"战争总有一天是要打的。（蓬无可奈何地举手向天。）宁可放在这个“打”字上，把第二个才放在和平上——PEACE（和平），不让就要丧失警惕。","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"5567d55aea"}],"page":{"id":"9d4bbaf0a6","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"5567d55aea","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}